    "Id": "732215",
    "ThreadId": "217305",
    "Html": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span>I think you're missing the actual DataTemplate in this code:</span></p>\n<div>\n<pre><span>&lt;</span><span>DataTemplate</span> <span>DataType</span><span>=</span>\"<span>{x:Type Sample:MSVertex}</span>\"<span>&gt;</span>\n        <span>&lt;</span><span>DataTemplate.Triggers</span><span>&gt;</span>\n        \t<span>&lt;</span><span>DataTrigger</span> <span>Binding</span><span>=</span>\"<span>{Binding Path=Status}</span>\" <span>Value</span><span>=</span>\"<span>1</span>\"<span>&gt;</span>\n                    <span>&lt;</span><span>Setter</span> <span>TargetName</span><span>=</span>\"<span>vertexBorder</span>\" <span>Property</span><span>=</span>\"<span>Backgroundcolor</span>\" <span>Value</span><span>=</span>\"<span>blue</span>\"<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;/</span><span>Setter</span><span>&gt;</span>\n                <span>&lt;/</span><span>DataTrigger</span><span>&gt;</span>\n\t<span>&lt;/</span><span>DataTemplate.Triggers</span><span>&gt;</span>\n<span>&lt;/</span><span>DataTemplate</span><span>&gt;</span></pre>\n</div>\n<div>See badang's example (it's the 5th message above your one), the releveant part (you're missing the emphasised border part):</div>\n<div>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataTemplate</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataType</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">{x:Type common_graph:EntityVertex}</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Border</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x:Name</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">vertexBorder</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">StackPanel</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ToolTip</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">{Binding  Path=Description}</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x:Name</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">vertexPanel</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TextBlock /</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;/</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">StackPanel</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;/</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Border</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataTemplate.Triggers</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataTrigger</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Binding</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">{Binding Path=IsSelected}</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Value</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">True</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Setter</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TargetName</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">vertexBorder</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Property</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BorderBrush</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Value</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Black</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Setter</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;/</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataTrigger</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;/</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataTemplate.Triggers</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;/</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataTemplate</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">ps: @labberlich: Your problem has nothing to do with Graph#.&nbsp;<span>If WPF is new for you, then you should start learning WPF (datatemplates, triggers, XAML, ...) - and ask those questions on a WPF forum.</span></span></p>\n</div>",
